sent.orig: Cell-to-Cell Mapping is one of the powerful instruments of the global analysis for non-linear dynamic system.
sent.trans: 胞映射(Cell-to-CellMapping)是对非线性动力系统进行全局分析的有力工具之一。

sent.orig: The analyse by C-CELL technology showed that loaves baking with sponge-dough method had finer internal texture.
sent.trans: 而C-CELL分析结果则表明中种发酵法烘焙的面包内部结构细腻。

sent.orig: OBJECTIVE:To study the clinicopathologicae,immunohistochemical characteristics and prognosis of subependymal giant-cell astrocytoma(SEGA).
sent.trans: 目的：探讨室管膜下巨细胞星形细胞瘤(subependymal giant-cell astrocytoma,SEGA)的临床病理特征、免疫表型特征及其与预后的关系。
